{"tid":1171419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漁人得利！越南引外資飆七成　港商佔最多","createTime":"2019-05-25T16:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T17:16:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"450ee4c39238661c4d709969732b5f32d83a60ff","tid":1171419,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190525/photo/bkn-20190525212113522-0525_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190525232529\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190525212113522-0525_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190525232529&h=73a6b40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿戰由去年打到今年，近月美國加徵華貨品關稅，更令戰事愈演愈烈；全球不少廠商都加速遷走在中國的生產線，越南正是箇中的受惠者之一。外媒引述越南計劃與投資部的數據指，2019年至今當地已承諾的外商直接投資(FDI)規模達167.4億美元，較2018年大幅長69.1%，並且創下4年新高。至於期內已到位的FDI金額亦達73億美元，按年增7.8%。<br />\n<br />\n數據又顯示，本年至今當地相關部門已簽發1,363項外商投資許可，金額達64.6億美元；另有505家外商獲准加大投資規模，涉及金額達26.3億美元。<br />\n<br />\n期內，香港廠商在當地的投資金額達50.8億美元，排名第一；其次則為南韓及新加坡的廠商，分別達26.2億美元及20.9億美元。至於中國及日本廠商則分居第四及第五位。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，早於貿易戰發生前，不少在華南地區設生產線的香港廠商已經因為成本急速上漲等問題，將廠房遷至東南亞；中美貿戰爆發，更令港商加速撤離，尤其是一些不需高科技生產技術，以及勞工密集的製造業，就更熱衷於遷廠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190525/bkn-20190525212113522-0525_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190525%2Fbkn-20190525212113522-0525_00842_001.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFNToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=d9593db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190525/bkn-20190525212113522-0525_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e2dcaf6875153b8049a59bdb7ba3c6403633ac57","tid":1171419,"uid":31076,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例通過之後<br />\n<br />\n依班港商都會喺祖國公平嘅審訊之下變哂做性罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9786d12e509db7427930d84cabb5ade9bc495eea","tid":1171419,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"樓價高企轉移越南<br />\n港樓價大跌五成<br />\n<br />\n有福了有福了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18ccc97846c3ed106fb060473ec440a892ebe18","tid":1171419,"uid":39181,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:52:52.000Z","msg":"香港人梗係幫襯返同種族既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3a0098d66759976616ff68b9b2c0856651cafb","tid":1171419,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"係時侯學定越南文"},{"pid":"14110226f4dff8e3abcf65bd3a769d86088982a2","tid":1171419,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"世界工廠去晒越南泰國柬埔寨啦<br />\n柬埔寨淫業同當年東莞有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757342a17998798ed9c41f881034185ffc0613de","tid":1171419,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"越南發大財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}